9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0&amp;oe=5DDE6B2B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3D85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0%26oe%3D5DDE6B2B&h=61e168b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖主義標籤係多國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名。正名警隊嘅恐怖主義絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c0f7d8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">44,009</span>/100,